d. The impact of the proposed mandate on the total cost of health care.
5. The legislative council shall contract with a private entity, after receiving one or more
recommendations from the insurance commissioner, to provide the legislative management
the cost-benefit analysis required by this section. The insurance commissioner shall pay the
cost of the contracted services to the entity providing the services.

